New Records: Travis Head scored an unbeaten 154 off 129 deliveries, his sixth ODI century
Key Match Events: Ben Duckett scored 95 off 91 balls for England
Harry Brook made his debut as captain for England, scoring 39 off 31 balls
Miscellaneous Highlights: Adam Zampa took 3/49, while Marnus Labuschagne contributed with the ball with 3/39 and Travis Head with 2/34
Others: The match was played at Trent Bridge in Nottingham
